RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: CONTRACT_REF_NO = (SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTB_CONTRACT C WHERE C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_MASTER.CONTRACT_REF_NO)

PAYER_PARTICIPANT = (SELECT PAYER_PARTICIPANT FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_MASTER C WHERE C.PAYER_PARTICIPANT = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.PAYER_PARTICIPANT AND C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT = (SELECT RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_MASTER D WHERE D.RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT AND D.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select a.participant,b.customer_name1,c.COMPONENT from lbtbs_contract_participant a,lftms_product_iccf c, /*oltm_customer b*/ (select customer_no customer_no,short_name customer_name1 FROM oltm_customer UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER customer_no,POSITION_IDENTIFIER_DESC customer_name1 FROM TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER) b where contract_ref_no= ? and contract_type='DR' AND a.participant = b.customer_no AND c.skim_component = 'Y' AND c.skim_pay_receive = 'R' AND c.product = (select participant_product from oltms_product_master_ld where product = ?) AND event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from lbtbs_contract_participant where contract_ref_no = ?)

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: EVENT_SEQ_NO IN (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS WHERE PAYER_PARTICIPANT = (SELECT PAYER_PARTICIPANT FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_MASTER C WHERE C.PAYER_PARTICIPANT = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.PAYER_PARTICIPANT AND C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT = (SELECT RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_MASTER D WHERE D.RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.RECEIVER_PARTICIPANT AND D.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND CONTRACT_REF_NO = (SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTB_CONTRACT E WHERE E.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND E.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO) GROUP BY VALUE_DATE)

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO, A.USER_REF_NO, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.COUNTERPARTY, A.BRANCH, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1, C.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B, OLTMS_PRODUCT C WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY AND C.PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTB_CONTRACT_SKIM_DETAILS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO)

select a.participant,b.customer_name1,c.COMPONENT from lbtbs_contract_participant a,lftms_product_iccf c, /*oltm_customer b*/ (select customer_no customer_no,short_name customer_name1 FROM oltm_customer UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER customer_no,POSITION_IDENTIFIER_DESC customer_name1 FROM TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER) b where contract_ref_no= ? and contract_type='DR' AND a.participant = b.customer_no AND c.skim_component = 'Y' AND c.skim_pay_receive = 'P' AND c.product = (select participant_product from oltms_product_master_ld where product = ?) AND event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from lbtbs_contract_participant where contract_ref_no = ?)
